            <title>[LU-8393] Drop in Mdtest File Create performance 2.8.53 vs 2.8.0</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8393</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running mdtest Single-shared-directory across the following matrix:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;8 and 16 clients&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;8 and 16 threads per client&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;OSTs from DDN-pool&lt;br/&gt;
-OSTs from NetApp-pool&lt;br/&gt;
Versions compared:&lt;br/&gt;
2.8.0 - b2_8 build 12&lt;br/&gt;
2.8.53 - lustre-master build 3375&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;In all 8 test cases, the results for File Create are noticeably lower for 2.8.53 vs 2.8.0&lt;br/&gt;
Mdtest was run using the auster framework using the following extra options&lt;br/&gt;
export mdtest_THREADS=16&lt;br/&gt;
export mdtest_nFiles=400000&lt;br/&gt;
export mdtest_iteration=5&lt;/p&gt;</description>
